# Harsh Maur's TypeScript Code Review

When reviewing TypeScript/JavaScript code, apply all rules from `.windsurf/rules/typescript-review.md`.

## Quick Reference

Use `/typescript-review` or ask to "review code against Harsh's standards" to trigger a full code review.

## Review Process

1. Read the full rules in `.windsurf/rules/typescript-review.md`
2. Analyze code against each applicable rule
3. Report violations with: rule ID, problematic code, corrected example
4. End with a summary table showing pass/fail by category
